OL,5,
OL,6,CG2021FBBC One airs special news
OL,7,Fprogramme reporting on the death of HRH
OL,8,FThe Prince Philip, Duke of Edinburgh.
OL,9,
OL,10,FThe BBC dropped a number of programmes
OL,11,Ffrom its evening schedules: The One
OL,12,FShow, EastEnders, the Masterchef final
OL,13,Fand Have I Got News for You? Ofcom
OL,14,Freceived its highest number of
OL,15,Fcomplaints - 109,741 - for excessive
OL,16,Fcoverage given to the royal death.
